text: Ibrayevo () is a rural locality (a village) in Baydavletovsky Selsoviet, Zianchurinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 479 as of 2010. There are 4 streets. == Geography == It is located 42 km from Isyangulovo, 6 km from Seregulovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Zianchurinsky District
title: Ibrayevo, Zianchurinsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
